n其實你地知唔知<br />\n吾, 係文言文即係「我」<br />\n<br />\n張圖寫住「錢, 吾係萬能」<br />\n即係「錢, 我係萬能」<br />\n<br />\n唔明你地嘈乜</blockquote><br />\n豬閪成又出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊個柒都未知<br />\n<br />\n吾<br />\n代詞<br />\n我。<br />\n我的。<br />\n普通話：w&uacute; 。 客家方言第一人稱代詞，讀：ng&aacute;i。 複數為：吾等、吾等人。 見《三國演義》第一回：其人曰：「吾姓關名羽......」 飛曰：「吾莊後有一桃園......」</blockquote><br />\n嘩屌你依下柒到同關家姐有得揮"},{"pid":"f2ea62e655b7a4dfe66b581c3b42f5e81e97fba6","tid":277651,"uid":50843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:30:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n已經特登改文個囉喎,仲想點?篇文原文都係&quot;吾吾吾&quot;架</blockquote><br />\n又唔係鬧樓主你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你地知唔知<br />\n吾, 係文言文即係「我」<br />\n<br />\n張圖寫住「錢, 吾係萬能」<br />\n即係「錢, 我係萬能」<br />\n<br />\n唔明你地嘈乜</blockquote><br />\n豬閪成又出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊個柒都未知<br />\n<br />\n吾<br />\n代詞<br />\n我。<br />\n我的。<br />\n普通話：w&uacute; 。 客家方言第一人稱代詞，讀：ng&aacute;i。 複數為：吾等、吾等人。 見《三國演義》第一回：其人曰：「吾姓關名羽......」 飛曰：「吾莊後有一桃園......」</blockquote><br />\n嘩屌你依下柒到同關家姐有得揮</blockquote><br />\n有讀過高中都知個吾字可以咁解啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係而家係咪咁嘅意思呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要柒多獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6927c7a170a4fcf89044ed8950af51ec7c41d82","tid":277651,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:30:31.000Z","msg":"字都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死撚左佢啦"},{"pid":"8489db55a667157c11ab93a72ba59edb9bf8c143","tid":277651,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:30:39.000Z","msg":"早幾年入行都無前途啦<br />\n<br />\n依條友應該入左去好多年"}]}